(- Standalone comparison helper; not integrated into live API path.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(4\) Why these specific choices instead of alternatives) Tj
T*
(- llama_cpp over transformers: direct GGUF support and lower resource overhead.) Tj
T*
(- SQLite over PostgreSQL: simpler local operations, zero external service dependency.) Tj
T*
(- Rule-based analyzer over learned policy: transparent and debuggable pruning decisions.) Tj
T*
(- Background thread trigger over task queue: low setup complexity; acceptable for local single-node) Tj
T*
(use.) Tj
T*
(- Static frontend over SPA framework: immediate deploy with FastAPI static mount and no build) Tj
T*
(tooling.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(5\) Known gaps and tradeoffs) Tj
T*
(- Structural telemetry is simulated, not real hidden-state instrumentation.) Tj
T*
(- Evolution recompilation is metadata simulation for GGUF copies, not true weight surgery.) Tj
T*
(- Some frontend-backend field expectations are loosely aligned and may drift.) Tj
T*
(- compare_models.py uses a different model family than TinyLlama flow.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(6\) Suggested future upgrades) Tj
T*
(- Split main.py into router modules.) Tj
T*
(- Add typed service layer between API and DB.) Tj
T*
(- Replace simulated telemetry with instrumented model internals \(if model/runtime supports it\).) Tj
T*
(- Add async job queue for evolution tasks.) Tj
T*
(- Add integration tests for endpoints and evolution gates.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(End of report.) Tj
T*
ET
endstream
